column3:
<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Bagnobrok is on the lookout for a widewalking adventurer.
Deliver the pungent pellets to Swipostik.
Pfff... pfffkohhh... You are an adventurer, are you not? One who widewalks from place to place?
If you intend to widewalk to Many Fires, could you give this to mobbiefriend Swipostik? Bagnobrok forgot to overhand it last time he visited.
Naturally, your service shall receive its just reward. Just one warnyword: do not hold noseclose! Very stinkystuff!
...What is the stinkystuff? It is better you don't know. Don't want to spoil Swipostik's surprise!
Pfffkohhh... A present from Bagnobrok, you say? I wonder what it could be...
Ah, what an uncredible aroma! Surewise, this is...yes, it is! The most farfamed of fancytastes that nomobbie can resist!
Why so wideeyes, adventurer? Did Bagnobrok not tell you what the present is? Swipostik could tell, but it would be better coming from Bagnobrok's wordhole. You should ask him!
No, adventurer, no! Swipostik will never lipslip Bagnobrok's secret!
You gave the present to Swipostik? Manythanks. Swipostik was very happyfeels about it, Bagnobrok trusts?

There isn't a Moblin around who doesn't love rot-tea, and Bagnobrok's rot-tea is very lipsmacky indeed. Put a pinch in a pot and boil it up, and the festergas is enough to make anymobbie's mask fill with eyewater!
Yes, rot-tea of Bagnobrok is very goodstuff. Bagnobrok knows exactly which fingerclippings and backscratchings make for the best brew.
Pfff? Why so bigeyes, adventurer? Do you want to try rot-tea of Bagnobrok for yourself? Sorry, but he gave it all to Swipostik! You will just have to wait until the next harvest!
